    "body" : "<p>An optimized Imran Tariq's version</p>\n\n<pre><code>Pattern.compile(strptrn, Pattern.CASE_INSENSITIVE + Pattern.LITERAL).matcher(str1).find();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Pattern.quote(strptrn) always returns \"\\Q\" + s + \"\\E\" even if there is nothing to quote, concatination spoils performance.</p>\n"
