  "title" : "String contains - ignore case",
  "body" : "<p>Is it possible to determine if a String <code>str1=\"ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOP\"</code> contains a string pattern <code>strptrn=\"gHi\"</code>? I wanted to know if that's possible when the characters are case insensitive. If so, how?</p>\n"
